{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2178, "height": 2962, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [160, 777, 246, 1546], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三二五", "block_bbox": [174, 2246, 231, 2379], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四世杜文炳：字重光，清代渑池著名乡绅，南五里里正。十四世杜化鹏：庠生。\n", "block_bbox": [358, 244, 1455, 379], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜作唐：又名佐唐，文炳子，北京政法大学堂毕业，县师范校长、县议会参议。见于县志。\n", "block_bbox": [356, 395, 1945, 532], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜生杰：西北军少校营长。", "block_bbox": [359, 627, 1005, 690], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜生新：少校军医、县人大代表。", "block_bbox": [360, 706, 1116, 768], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜振乾：国外医院院长。", "block_bbox": [361, 784, 962, 844], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜振范：渑池县人民银行干部。1988年始据云和神轴纂王都杜氏入总谱。", "block_bbox": [359, 860, 1915, 922], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜学成：郑州市商业专科学校教授。", "block_bbox": [363, 1012, 1185, 1071], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜黎明：振范子，曾任渑池城市信用社主任、渑池县农村信用社副主任、义马市农村信用社主任等职。\n", "block_bbox": [359, 1086, 1947, 1217], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜灵梅：振范女，本科。县一高教师。", "block_bbox": [362, 1234, 1205, 1295], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜发学：国营七七仓库经理。", "block_bbox": [363, 1309, 1094, 1370], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜淑霞：女，大学毕业，县水利局干部。", "block_bbox": [363, 1383, 1228, 1445], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜建成：国玺子，大专毕业，县史志办编辑。中国唐史学会会员、中国武则天研究会会员、河南省地方史志协会会员，《渑池县志》《渑池年鉴》主编。", "block_bbox": [360, 1461, 1946, 1597], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜万祥：大专毕业，陕县化工厂干部。", "block_bbox": [364, 1608, 1208, 1670], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "长门窑湾：", "block_bbox": [366, 1685, 581, 1744], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "七世杜璋：明未时，领兵下云南。其原配李氏仍居渑池，卒葬大块地。据传，后裔定居于今云南省漾鼻县，情况失传。\n", "block_bbox": [360, 1760, 1947, 1896], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜承天：监生。", "block_bbox": [365, 1909, 784, 1968], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜万山：清同治(1862~1874)时，当洪秀全起义，渑池知县派款太重，农民被逼起义，选公为首领，群起反抗官府，公被定为“反贼”，在封建统治镇压下壮烈牺牲。\n", "block_bbox": [362, 1984, 1951, 2194], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜宗义：曾任甘肃省会宁县粮食局长。", "block_bbox": [368, 2210, 1235, 2270], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜平泉：中学地理高级教师。详修祠续谱功德碑。", "block_bbox": [368, 2286, 1454, 2345], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜双锁：中学数学高级教师。", "block_bbox": [368, 2361, 1057, 2418], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜二祥：三门峡水电学校毕业，后任教师。", "block_bbox": [368, 2436, 1302, 2494], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜苏民：企业家。立足渑池，经营致富，富不忘本，克敦族谊，参与修祠续谱。详修祠续谱功德碑。\n", "block_bbox": [364, 2509, 1943, 2638], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜俊清：函授本科，任绳池县工商局副书记。", "block_bbox": [368, 2656, 1344, 2714], "block_id": 24, "block_order": 25}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7256268858909607, "coordinate": [362.00067138671875, 1984.35986328125, 1951.242919921875, 2194.2216796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6400442123413086, "coordinate": [360.113037109375, 1760.19384765625, 1947.173095703125, 1896.6376953125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6283214688301086, "coordinate": [356.1744384765625, 395.6544189453125, 1945.7122802734375, 532.3740844726562]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5943044424057007, "coordinate": [359.54437255859375, 1086.980224609375, 1947.030029296875, 1217.4560546875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5919448733329773, "coordinate": [364.80047607421875, 2509.82958984375, 1943.48046875, 2638.50146484375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5647953152656555, "coordinate": [360.50799560546875, 1461.77978515625, 1946.979248046875, 1597.275146484375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5510402321815491, "coordinate": [368.39794921875, 2436.4345703125, 1302.41552734375, 2494.083984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.526731014251709, "coordinate": [368.5818176269531, 2656.41064453125, 1344.57763671875, 2714.84814453125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5258758068084717, "coordinate": [368.44122314453125, 2286.01171875, 1454.686767578125, 2345.3232421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5227212309837341, "coordinate": [365.5791015625, 1909.7340087890625, 784.849609375, 1968.8128662109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5204543471336365, "coordinate": [368.5863342285156, 2361.112060546875, 1057.6636962890625, 2418.235107421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5091192722320557, "coordinate": [368.735107421875, 2210.79931640625, 1235.18017578125, 2270.03369140625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "l